    <item>
      <title>巴基斯坦通胀放缓，创纪录的通胀率减缓了生活成本的增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/pakistan-inflation-eases-as-record-rates-slow-living-cost-gains</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于能源价格上涨和货币贬值，创纪录的高利率对生活成本产生了更大的影响，巴基斯坦一月份的通胀率有所放缓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/pakistan-inflation-eases-as-record-rates-slow-living-cost-gains</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 10:49:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧元区物价放缓幅度低于预期，给欧洲央行降息蒙上阴影</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/eurozone-inflation-slows-less-than-expected-clouding-rate-cut-hopes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧元区通胀放缓程度低于年初预期——测试投资者对欧洲央行最早将于春季开始降息的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/eurozone-inflation-slows-less-than-expected-clouding-rate-cut-hopes</guid>
